title: 623. Which Team Stocks to Buy from Top 5 of 2021 NFL Draft
itunes:title: 623. Which Team Stocks to Buy from Top 5 of 2021 NFL Draft
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a special new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys look at the current teams picking in the top 5 of the 2021 NFL Draft and each pick which team's stock they would buy (2:25). Then, the duo explain why coaches should have experience building a program and developing players (20:09). To wrap up the show, the pair discuss the Philadelphia Eagles naming quarterback Jalen Hurts their starter for this week and compare quarterback Carson Wentz's career to the early career of former NFL quarterback Peyton Manning (26:40). Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
